[quote]
Wiki That! is a mod which provides tools to quickly access wiki pages related to various aspects of Project Zomboid, directly from in-game. It adds context menu options to items, fluids, vehicles, and other game elements.

Direct support for [url=https://pzwiki.net]pzwiki.net[/url] links is present in the game, thus increasing the Wiki pages access from inside the game.
[/quote]

[h1]How to use[/h1]
[list]
[*]Right-click on an item, fluid, vehicle part, or other game element to open the context menu.
[*]Look for the "Wiki That!" option in the context menu.
[*]Click on "Wiki That!" to open the corresponding wiki page in your web browser or Steam overlay if activated.
[/list]

[h3]A few tips ![/h3]
[list]
[*]Selecting multiple items will open all of them in a submenu instead to access each individual unique items wiki pages.
[*]The game will be paused when opening a wiki page but you can disable it in the mod options menu.
[*]Wiki pages will open in the Steam overlay by default if it is activated, or in the browser otherwise or if you enabled the option in the mod options menu for it.
[/list]

