[h1]Supported game elements[/h1]
[list]
[*]Items.
[*]VHS and other medias in the inventory.
[*]Fluids inside items.
[*]Moveable tiles (as items in the inventory).
[*]Vehicles.
[*]Foraging icons.
[*]Traits in the character creation menu.
[*]Animals.
[*]World objects (crops, tiles).
[*]Moodles.
[/list]

